TOUCH: Atlantean Tattoo Activation

Syntax: touch <location> tattoo [target]

Activates the magical tattoo inscribed on one of your body locations.

BODY LOCATIONS:
  right forearm    left forearm
  right upper arm  left upper arm
  right hand       left hand
  chest            back
  right shoulder   left shoulder
  right leg        left leg
  right calf       left calf
  neck             face

EXAMPLES:
  touch right forearm tattoo
      Activates whatever tattoo is inscribed on your right forearm.

  touch right hand tattoo goblin
      Activates a ranged attack tattoo (fire bolt, flaming arrow) and
      fires it at 'goblin' in the room.

TATTOO TYPES:
  Weapon   - Summons a physical magical weapon. Uses PPE.
  Armor    - Creates a temporary MDC field. Uses PPE.
  Power    - Various effects (light, healing, sight, stealth). Uses PPE.
  Passive  - Always active. No activation needed. No PPE cost.

PPE COST:
  Activating a tattoo drains PPE. PPE regenerates over time, or faster
  in meditation. If you do not have enough PPE, the tattoo does not fire.

ALREADY ACTIVE:
  Timed tattoos (armor, some power) will report their remaining time
  if you try to activate them while already running.

NOTE:
  Combat restrictions apply to some tattoos (super healing cannot be
  used while in combat).

